{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS格線布局","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS\"><strong>CSS</strong></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\"><strong>CSS 參考</strong></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">CSS 格線布局</a></li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>參考</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">格線布局基本概念</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Relationship_of_Grid_Layout\">與其他布局的關系</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">基於行展示的位置</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">格線模板區域</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Layout_using_Named_Grid_Lines\">使用指定網格線布局</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Auto-placement_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">自動放置格線布局</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Box_Alignment_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">格線布局中的框對齊</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid,_Logical_Values_and_Writing_Modes\">格線，邏輯值和寫入模式</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Layout_and_Accessibility\">CSS 格線布局和輔助功能</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_and_Progressive_Enhancement\">CSS 格線布局與漸進式增強</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Realizing_common_layouts_using_CSS_Grid_Layout\">使用格線實現常見的布局</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Properties</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\">網格</a> </li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\">網格區域</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\">網格自動列</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\">網格自動流</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\">網格自動行</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\">網格列</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\">結束網格列</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-gap\">網格柱間隙</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\">啟動網格</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-gap\">網格間隙</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\">網格行</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\">結束網格行</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-gap\">網格行間隙</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\">啟動網格行</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\">網格模板</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\">網格模板區域</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\">網格模板的列</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\">網格模板的行</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>詞匯表</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid\">格線</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid_lines\">網格線</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid_tracks\">網格軌道</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid_cell\">網格單元格</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid_areas\">網格區域</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Gutters\">间距</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid_Axis\">網格軸</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid_rows\">網格行</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid_column\">網格列</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS 格線佈局</strong>長於把頁面的主要區域分離、或是在 HTML 原生語法構建的區域間，定義大小、位置、層次等方面的關聯。</p>\n\n<p>格線佈局使作者能夠對齊元素為行和列，就像表格一樣，。然而，格線佈局可以更輕易的達成比一般表格更多元化的排版。例如，一個網格容器的子元素可以定位自己和層重疊，類似於CSS定位元素。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"basic_example","title":"基本示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下示例展示了一個三列軌道格線，其中創建的行數最小為 100 像素，最大為 auto。Items 已經使用基於線放置在網格的位置上。</p>\n\n<div id=\"example\">\n\n\n<h3 id=\"html\">HTML</h3>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>one<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>One<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>two<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Two<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>three<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Three<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>four<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Four<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>five<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Five<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>six<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Six<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<h3 id=\"css\">CSS</h3>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-auto-rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.one</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-column</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1 / 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.two</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-column</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2 / 4<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1 / 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.three</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2 / 5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-column</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.four</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-column</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.five</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-column</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.six</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-column</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"500\" height=\"440\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參考","title":"參考","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_屬性","title":"CSS 屬性","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect2\">\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid\"><code>grid</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\"><code>grid-row-start</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\"><code>grid-column-start</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\"><code>grid-row-end</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\"><code>grid-column-end</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\"><code>grid-row</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\"><code>grid-column</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\"><code>grid-row-gap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\"><code>grid-column-gap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/gap\"><code>grid-gap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_函式","title":"CSS 函式","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect3\">\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/repeat\"><code>repeat()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/minmax\"><code>minmax()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/fit-content\"><code>fit-content()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_資料型別","title":"CSS 資料型別","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect4\">\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/flex_value\"><code>&lt;flex&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"詞匯表條目","title":"詞匯表條目","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect5\">\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Grid\">格線</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Lines\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">網格線 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Tracks\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">格線軌道 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Cell\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">格線單元 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">格線區域 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">間距 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Axis\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">格線軸 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">格線行 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Column\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">格線列 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"指引","title":"指引","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect6\">\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">格線布局的基本概念</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layo